BinarySearchTrees

Class BSTNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • BinarySearchTrees.BSTNode

  • public class BSTNode
extends java.lang.Object
    CSCI 333, Homework 6: Binary Search Trees. Implementation of individual nodes of the binary search tree with BSTNodes inside of it relating it to its parent, its left child, and its right child as well as an integer for storing it's key value.
